    "value": "DEFINE MODEL ShellyDeviceStatus WITH TOPIC \"ShellyDevice/+/status\""
  },
  {
    "kind": 1,
    "language": "markdown",
    "value": "üí° + is used as a wildcard to match any Shelly device name.\r\n\r\nüö® Action: High Current Alert\r\nThis action listens to the parsed model ShellyDeviceStatus and sends a warning if the current exceeds 0.5A.\r\n\r\n"
